WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:03.190
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.590
Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.310
Well, glory to God. I wasn't going

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:10.870
to do a video today, but there's things

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:13.150
on my heart that I would like to talk

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:16.630
about. Diana is behind the camera. Hi.

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:20.230
And she said, "Honey, after you did

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:21.990
that video last night and the anointing

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.310
was so strong in the house and we were

00:00:25.310 --> 00:00:25.320
interceding,"she

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:27.750
says, "it's

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:29.910
been on my heart all day

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:29.920
long."You

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:34.790
know, she's Apache

00:00:34.790 --> 00:00:34.800
and

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:37.510
about the Trail of Tears and

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:39.110
all of it, you know, about her ancestors

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:42.590
and the Trail of Tears and

00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:45.510
the Native Americans and the suffering

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:47.270
that they went through, you know, and

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:50.069
all the different things,

00:00:50.079 --> 00:00:54.470
the hardship of people.

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:56.950
But she said, "I feel in my spirit

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:59.510
there's something more to what you saw

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:01.510
about the African-American population

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:03.029
last night, Brandon, and I don't

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:04.950
know what it is, but I'm going to start

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:07.429
searching. I want to study because I

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:08.950
feel the spirit of the Lord has told me

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.750
there's more."And so, she was sitting

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:14.230
on the couch and she started just,

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:16.310
you know, my wife's very intelligent and

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.630
she's over there tapping away and she

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:21.190
goes, "Oh, I found it."She came to me

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.390
and she was crying, and she said,

00:01:22.390 --> 00:01:22.400
"Brandon,

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:24.390
I found it."She said,

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.469
"Everything the Lord,"she goes, "the

00:01:26.479 --> 00:01:28.510
Lord is so strategic in

00:01:28.510 --> 00:01:28.520
timing."She

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:30.630
goes, "Brandon, we live in

00:01:30.630 --> 00:01:30.640
Tulsa."And

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.270
she said, "I just found the

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:37.510
Tulsa race riots started on May 31st of

00:01:39.560 --> 00:01:43.510
1921, and they went until June

00:01:43.510 --> 00:01:43.520
1st."And

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:46.550
she said 30 blocks of homes were burned

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:49.030
from African-American men and

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:51.270
women, businesses, everything. And they

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.270
called it Black Wall Street. It was a

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:55.190
wealthier part of one of the wealthiest

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:59.030
black suburbs in America at the time.

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:02.709
And there were 800 people that were hurt.

00:02:02.709 --> 00:02:02.719
Several—I

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:05.270
think it was like 30, 40

00:02:05.270 --> 00:02:05.280
people—lost

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:09.270
their lives. 36 total: 26

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:12.030
African-Americans and 10 white.

00:02:12.040 --> 00:02:17.589
Yep. A very tragic thing.

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:21.910
And I just, wow, what was on, you know,

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:25.030
when I come, you know, I

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:27.430
let you in on something that's so

00:02:27.440 --> 00:02:30.550
private to Diana and me, our prayer time.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:33.190
You don't allow—it's very,

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:35.750
for me, it's taken a learning

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:37.430
curve for me to let people in because

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:40.309
this is my walk that I've had

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.550
since I've been

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:44.509
16. It's something I've

00:02:44.519 --> 00:02:48.229
developed. And when you sit

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:52.869
at the Father's feet, He shows you

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:55.949
what's on His

00:02:55.959 --> 00:02:58.710
heart. He shows you what's on His heart.

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:01.070
He shows you what He's compassionate

00:03:01.070 --> 00:03:01.080
about—things

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:04.270
that you think have been

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:06.630
forgotten. Things like—I saw

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:08.869
whenever I was in the spirit, I saw a

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:12.470
rug, a big-looking rug, a throw rug, and

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.070
it was being lifted up and it was

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:16.149
used like a dustpan, and people

00:03:16.149 --> 00:03:16.159
wanted

00:03:16.159 --> 00:03:18.229
to brush all the dirt underneath

00:03:18.229 --> 00:03:18.239
it.

00:03:18.239 --> 00:03:20.790
And He said, "I'm going to take that

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:23.190
rug up and I'm exposing the darkness, and

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:25.270
I'm exposing the dirt underneath

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:28.710
that rug."Brandon, the hurt, the pain

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:31.229
is real and it still exists in a lot of

00:03:31.239 --> 00:03:34.229
people. And I'm ready to heal it. I'm

00:03:34.239 --> 00:03:37.110
ready to set these people free. But not

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:41.270
only that, I saw Harriet Tubman, the

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:43.110
African-American woman with the

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:45.390
purple durag, and it was amazing,

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:51.030
folks, is that I saw pictures of

00:03:51.030 --> 00:03:51.040
her—my

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:52.869
son Googled her and we started

00:03:52.869 --> 00:03:52.879
looking—with

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:55.509
purple durags just like I

00:03:55.519 --> 00:03:57.429
saw, with the white shirt, when she was

00:03:57.439 --> 00:04:00.750
doing the Underground

00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:03.429
Railroad. But they called it Black Wall

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:05.670
Street. And if you remember last night,

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:09.270
I kept seeing Wall Street, Wall Street,

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:12.070
and I saw New York City. And that was

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:15.509
how the Lord was describing to

00:04:15.509 --> 00:04:15.519
me—not

00:04:15.519 --> 00:04:18.469
about New York City, it was a type and

00:04:18.479 --> 00:04:20.390
shadow of something that He was, because

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:22.629
I'm seeing New York being painted in

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:25.270
front of my face. But He doesn't tell me

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:26.950
"Tulsa Wall Street"because I wouldn't

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.830
have understood. He was talking

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:33.110
to me directly about Wall Street in New

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:35.270
York, and it was a type and shadow of

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:38.230
what was going on with the race riots in

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:40.790
Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:51.070
And my mind

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:54.670
was—I'm

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:58.150
humbled that He would want to take a

00:04:58.160 --> 00:05:05.310
bald-headed white

00:05:05.320 --> 00:05:09.029
guy, come on YouTube, and

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:11.749
want me to pray for

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:16.830
something so precious to

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:30.990
Him. I don't know why

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:33.550
me, all

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:54.189
these people.

00:05:54.199 --> 00:05:57.110
God, what He allowed me to see last

00:05:57.120 --> 00:06:02.710
night,

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:07.309
none of you can understand

00:06:07.319 --> 00:06:10.390
it. Even the African-American people

00:06:10.400 --> 00:06:12.870
that are here right now have a glimpse

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:15.990
of what you've heard.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:19.189
But I went into the depth of the heart

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:24.670
of it in the

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:32.510
spirit, and I could feel it in

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:34.909
intercession. Those people in

00:06:34.919 --> 00:06:38.749
chains and the pain they felt, so

00:06:38.759 --> 00:06:41.749
much God would give me glimpses of their

00:06:41.759 --> 00:06:47.430
heart.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:49.830
And words can't explain to you the

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:52.749
bondage and the hopelessness that they

00:06:52.759 --> 00:06:55.189
felt, similar to, I'm sure, what the

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:58.350
children of Israel felt for 400

00:06:58.360 --> 00:07:02.150
years. But people, you can read a

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:04.230
story, you can read a novel, you can

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:06.469
read history books. That's what I'm

00:07:06.479 --> 00:07:07.830
trying to say. You can read history

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.909
books, and you can hear about

00:07:09.919 --> 00:07:14.550
this woman with the purple rag, and we

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:17.510
all think she's great, or

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.510
Rosa Parks sitting in the back of

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:21.510
the bus. These people, we hear about them,

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.830
and maybe somebody might have known

00:07:23.830 --> 00:07:23.840
them,

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:27.990
but a

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:30.950
story is nothing until you feel it.

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:33.990
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:37.029
The Trail of Tears, I was there in the

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:39.270
spirit realm. I could see the children.

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.589
I could see these people walking in the

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:44.070
snow. I could see they were barefoot and

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:46.230
their feet were blistering with

00:07:47.880 --> 00:07:51.230
frostbite walking across the

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:54.309
land. And I could see them, and they were

00:07:54.309 --> 00:07:54.319
so—they

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:56.469
were tied up and they were going

00:07:56.479 --> 00:07:59.510
across the land, getting taken out of

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:02.309
their area where they lived to be

00:08:02.309 --> 00:08:02.319
taken

00:08:02.319 --> 00:08:03.790
to Oklahoma, to these

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:06.390
places, forced to leave, forced to do

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:09.670
these things. It's pain

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:12.710
beyond anybody's comprehension,

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:13.710
if it was

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:16.070
mine. And I'm not going to say here,

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:17.749
"Well, I can relate, I can do all

00:08:17.749 --> 00:08:17.759
this."No,

00:08:17.759 --> 00:08:19.469
no, no. I saw a

00:08:19.479 --> 00:08:23.510
glimpse. It's like opening up a book and

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:25.270
you see it, and you open it up, you get a

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:27.350
glimpse of something. But it's that way

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:29.230
in the spirit. I got a glimpse of

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:31.430
something, something that was very

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:35.430
hurtful. And me as a white guy,

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:36.509
I,

00:08:36.519 --> 00:08:38.790
like I said, I don't know why He

00:08:38.800 --> 00:08:43.269
chose me, but I am humbled, and

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:46.230
I know what the Lord said.

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:48.430
He said, "I've not forgotten your

00:08:48.430 --> 00:08:48.440
prayers,"and

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:51.190
I've heard that echo inside

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:53.230
of my spirit. And I could see the

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:55.910
prayers coming up from those African

00:08:55.920 --> 00:08:58.470
slaves in those camps with these wood

00:08:58.480 --> 00:09:00.870
huts, and they had little fires, and

00:09:00.880 --> 00:09:03.509
they were looking at the stars and they

00:09:03.519 --> 00:09:05.110
were looking at the North. And it was

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:07.350
interesting because that Tubman lady, it was

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.030
about the North Star. I could see the

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:10.470
North Star. I could see the Big Dipper.

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:12.230
I could see they were navigating by

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.870
stars at night to get through because they

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:17.190
didn't travel in the day. So, they were

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:19.509
trying to get through in the nighttime

00:09:19.519 --> 00:09:21.750
and they were using the stars as a map

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.110
so they wouldn't get lost. And that's

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:24.630
what I was seeing in the spirit. But

00:09:24.640 --> 00:09:27.389
they were looking for the North

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:29.430
Star. And I thought that was really

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.670
interesting because that's how detailed

00:09:31.680 --> 00:09:34.310
these visions were last night. I

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.870
could see them, and they had little bitty

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:38.870
fire torches, and they were trying to

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:41.110
move through areas, and I was

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:44.430
like, "What in the world,

00:09:44.430 --> 00:09:44.440
Lord?"And

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:48.150
as I'm looking and able

00:09:48.160 --> 00:09:51.110
to look over there, I see them praying

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:53.070
and singing old

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:58.630
songs. And there were

00:09:58.630 --> 00:09:58.640
old—not

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:01.430
Pentecostal songs, but old Bible songs

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:04.710
like hymnals, old hymns, old songs that

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:06.550
we don't sing anymore. I was

00:10:06.560 --> 00:10:08.070
trying to listen because I was hearing,

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:10.470
and this is what's amazing: I've never

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:13.509
been in a vision and heard people

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:15.670
singing before.

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:19.829
I could hear the African-American

00:10:19.839 --> 00:10:22.110
people

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:24.870
singing, the women and the men, and it was

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:25.870
a

00:10:25.880 --> 00:10:28.670
deep, heavy

00:10:28.680 --> 00:10:34.030
song. It wasn't joyful. It was

00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:35.870
heavy, like

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:39.910
groanings in the spirit. It was heavy,

00:10:39.920 --> 00:10:42.949
asking the Father for freedom. "Where are

00:10:42.959 --> 00:10:45.190
you? Why have you forgotten us? Why are

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:47.509
we going through this?"crying out for the

00:10:47.519 --> 00:10:51.790
Father to redeem them and set them

00:10:51.800 --> 00:10:55.829
free. And as I saw them praying, I saw

00:10:55.839 --> 00:10:59.069
a man named Abraham

00:10:59.079 --> 00:11:01.750
Lincoln. And God raised up a man named

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:03.150
Abraham

00:11:03.160 --> 00:11:07.670
Lincoln to do what he did to bring

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:09.630
freedom to the

00:11:09.640 --> 00:11:13.430
slaves. And I saw them murder him.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:15.829
I saw all this stuff panned out, and he

00:11:15.839 --> 00:11:18.069
was a really tall man, and some people

00:11:18.079 --> 00:11:21.190
say, "Well, he was 6'4","but with his top

00:11:21.190 --> 00:11:21.200
hat—I

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:23.670
saw his hat,

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:25.190
and it made him look like he

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.710
was a lot bigger. I'm telling you in the

00:11:26.710 --> 00:11:26.720
vision—and

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:29.269
this is another

00:11:29.269 --> 00:11:29.279
thing—was

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:32.150
everybody else a lot smaller? Because he

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:33.829
looked like he was head and shoulders

00:11:33.839 --> 00:11:36.870
above everybody, from these men that were

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.790
below him. So I'm like, well, maybe people

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:40.630
weren't very tall back then. I don't

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:43.190
know, because when I saw him, he was

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:45.829
like a really big guy in this black

00:11:45.839 --> 00:11:47.910
suit in the vision, and I'm still trying

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:49.430
to figure out what I saw. I'm like, was

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:51.670
he standing next to kids? I don't know.

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:53.269
All I know is I tell you these things,

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:55.750
but I saw he was a lot bigger of a man

00:11:55.760 --> 00:11:58.630
than everybody else was. So maybe

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:01.030
everybody else is like

00:12:01.030 --> 00:12:01.040
5'5"or

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:02.470
something. I don't know. They didn't

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:05.790
look like they were very big

00:12:05.800 --> 00:12:08.389
people. Does it matter? No. I just

00:12:08.389 --> 00:12:08.399
try

00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:10.310
to figure it out.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:13.030
I love when the Lord shows me things,

00:12:13.040 --> 00:12:16.310
and I take it very seriously. It's

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:18.310
His love language

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:21.230
towards me. It's

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:23.990
intimacy. It's how I learn

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:25.790
how to communicate with

00:12:25.800 --> 00:12:28.670
Him. And He shows me

00:12:28.680 --> 00:12:31.350
things. And it's something

00:12:31.360 --> 00:12:33.350
that I never thought I would ever

00:12:33.350 --> 00:12:33.360
go

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:35.949
public about to the point like I am

00:12:35.959 --> 00:12:38.870
now, that 70,000 people would look

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:42.110
at it a

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:44.949
day. But I know a lot of you are just

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:47.030
desperate and want intimacy with Him.

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:49.910
That's why you're here. You want your

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:52.470
own relationship. And the Lord wants you

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:55.230
to have it. He's no respecter of

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:57.829
persons, but He is a respecter of those

00:12:57.839 --> 00:13:00.389
that seek Him.

00:13:00.399 --> 00:13:02.790
And I want to tell you, as you seek Him,

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:03.790
you'll find

00:13:03.800 --> 00:13:06.590
Him. But when He told

00:13:06.600 --> 00:13:11.550
me He was going to

00:13:11.560 --> 00:13:15.590
bring a

00:13:15.590 --> 00:13:15.600
restitution—restitution,

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:19.509
but with interest. With interest. And

00:13:19.519 --> 00:13:20.870
people say, 'Well, how's that going to

